_sText:
This is my first Gun Game map. I obviously did not spend a lot of time on this version of the map. This version is only in beta, I plan to drastically boost the look and gameplay features of this map. All I need to do this is some feedback, constructive would be most sufficient. This map includes:
  • Custom Textures
  • Custom Skybox
  • Close Encounter Spots
  • Two Levels
  • Lots of Green! Please report any bugs or errors when playing the map and I'll do my best to fix them. Have my map in your rotation? Post here and let me know, I'll add your server to the list! Regards, Dotty
